      "标题": "Face4RAG: Factual Consistency Evaluation for Retrieval Augmented Generation in Chinese",
      "作者": ["Yunqi Xu", "Tianchi Cai", "Jiyan Jiang", "Xierui Song"],
      "发表时间": "2024-07-01",
